===Adjective===
'''unreadable''' (''[[comparative]]'' '''more unreadable''', ''[[superlative]]'' '''most unreadable''')

#That cannot be read or is not easy to read.
#:''unreadable handwriting''
#:''a machine that cut up secret documents into small unreadable fragments''
#:''unreadable charts''
#Not sufficiently interesting to be worth reading.
#:''unreadable book''

====Synonyms====
*(''that cannot be read or is not easy to read''): [[illegible]], [[indecipherable]], [[unclear]], [[undecipherable]]
*(''not sufficiently interesting to be worth reading''): [[boring]], [[dull]], [[tedious]]

